'''小火蟻'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{snamei|Wasmannia auropunctata}}，{{lang-en|electric ant}}、{{lang|en|little fire ant}}），又稱'''金刻沃氏蚁'''或'''光點小火蟻'''，是一種小型的[[切葉蟻|家蟻亞科]]物種，原生於中南美洲，現已擴張到北美洲、[[台灣|台灣]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=光點小火蟻 (''Wasmannia auropunctata'') (膜翅目：蟻科)：台灣新記錄之入侵螞蟻及其潛在威脅|author=李錦城、徐伯瑋、許峰銓、施鈞瀚、蕭祐鈞、楊景程、林宗岐|journal=台灣昆蟲|issn=2414-1194|doi=10.6662/TESFE.202108_41(3).004|doi-access=free|year=2021|volume=41|issue=3|pages=172-181}}</ref>、[[以色列|以色列]]<ref>{{cite journal|last=Vonshak|first=Merav|title=The little fire ant ''Wasmannia auropunctata'': a new invasive species in the Middle East and its impact on the local arthropod fauna|coauthors=T. Dayan, A. Ionescu-Hirsch, A. Freidberg, A. Hefetz|journal=Biological Invasions|year=2010|volume=12|pages=1825–1837|url=http://www.springerlink.com/content/n57t18648k7m5540/}}{{Dead link|date=2020年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Foucaud|first=Julien|coauthors=et al|title=Worldwide invasion by the little fire ant: routes of introduction and eco-evolutionary pathways|journal=Evolutionary Applications|year=2010|volume=3|pages=363–374}}</ref> 和一些[[太平洋島嶼|太平洋島嶼]]（[[加拉帕戈斯群島|加拉帕戈斯群島]]、[[夏威夷|夏威夷]]、[[新喀里多尼亞|新喀里多尼亞]]和[[所羅門群島|所羅門群島]]），此外東北澳大利亞的[[凱恩斯_(昆士蘭州)|凱恩]]亦有紀錄。<ref name="QldDPI01">[http://www.dpi.qld.gov.au/cps/rde/dpi/hs.xsl/4790_6453_ENA_HTML.htm Electric ant (''Wasmannia auropunctata'') webpage] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090214085035/http://dpi.qld.gov.au/cps/rde/dpi/hs.xsl/4790_6453_ENA_HTML.htm |date=2009-02-14 }} Accessed 7 March 2009</ref><ref name="Globaldbase01">{{Cite web |url=http://www.issg.org/database/species/search.asp?st=100ss&fr=1&str |title=Global Invasive Species Database - No. 100 - ''Wasmannia auropunctata'' |accessdate=2014-03-31 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116134944/http://www.issg.org/database/species/search.asp?st=100ss&fr=1&str |dead-url=no }}</ref>

其英文名稱“electric ant”來自其咬傷產生如[[觸電|觸電]]的強烈痛感，<ref name="QldWarning01">[http://www.mitchell-river.com.au/news-and-issues/27888_electric_ant_web.pdf Queensland Government Electric Ant: Warning] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110218112416/http://mitchell-river.com.au/news-and-issues/27888_electric_ant_web.pdf |date=2011-02-18 }} Accessed 7 March 2009</ref> 它也是[[世界百大外來入侵種|世界百大外來入侵種]]之一。小火蟻體長約1.5毫米，通體黃褐色。雌雄皆能[[無性繁殖|無性繁殖]]，是最早被發現兩性都可以無性繁殖的動物。<ref name= Fournier2005>{{cite journal |last1=Fournier |first1=Denis |last2=Estoup |first2=Arnaud |last3=Orivel |first3=Jérôme |last4=Foucaud |first4=Julien |last5=Jourdan |first5=Hervé |last6=Breton |first6=Julien Le |last7=Keller |first7=Laurent |title=Clonal reproduction by males and females in the little fire ant |journal=Nature |volume=435 |issue=7046 |pages=1230–4 |year=2005 |pmid=15988525 |doi=10.1038/nature03705}}</ref><ref name=Fournier2005/><ref name=Pearcy2004>{{cite journal |last1=Pearcy |first1=M. |last2=Aron |first2=S |last3=Doums |first3=C |last4=Keller |first4=L |title=Conditional Use of Sex and Parthenogenesis for Worker and Queen Production in Ants |journal=Science |volume=306 |issue=5702 |pages=1780–3 |year=2004 |pmid=15576621 |doi=10.1126/science.1105453}}</ref>

